{
  "3205380": {
    "name": "你有饼吗？",
    "steam_appid": 3205380,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/99affde3a6a83d878862d3e31f5c4809.poster.avif?t=1772358209\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/99affde3a6a83d878862d3e31f5c4809.webm?t=1772358209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/99affde3a6a83d878862d3e31f5c4809.mp4?t=1772358209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这所奇怪的学校里，你是食堂的新厨师。你的任务是做出完美的煎蛋卷。问题是，传送带上飞来的食材包括：新鲜水果、奶酪、辣椒……还有整颗椰子、扳手，以及一只会跳走的章鱼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更大的问题是，校长是一只很难讨好的鸡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/58a7b534edd1a57864fd118f4033cd35.avif?t=1772358209\" width=800 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/a220c76fb9ea436fb3c9a5d2c1a2bc45.poster.avif?t=1772358209\" width=960 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/a220c76fb9ea436fb3c9a5d2c1a2bc45.webm?t=1772358209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/a220c76fb9ea436fb3c9a5d2c1a2bc45.mp4?t=1772358209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亲手把食材摆到大饼上。食材之间会互相影响：辣椒点燃一切、奶酪叠加倍率、相同类别触发连击。摆放位置决定得分高低——而且放下的东西不能再拿起来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高难度下传送带飞速运转，蛋饼会旋转缩小，顾客还会偷你的食材、往饼里扔垃圾。你需要在混乱中快速决策、精准操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不喜欢时间压力？可以开启回合制模式，用你自己的节奏享受游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/784e932cea33167e5f5ec92f5cc55096.avif?t=1772358209\" width=800 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/45fdadad0a5f103e539033ab92523dfe.avif?t=1772358209\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位顾客都有独特的口味和怪癖。上一秒你还在做经典的青椒培根卷饼，下一秒就要往里塞甜甜圈、酸黄瓜和巧克力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >至于扳手、煤炭、易拉罐？别问，问就是鸡校长满意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/abbabc8442cbefaace27951d6c3a863e.poster.avif?t=1772358209\" width=900 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/abbabc8442cbefaace27951d6c3a863e.webm?t=1772358209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/abbabc8442cbefaace27951d6c3a863e.mp4?t=1772358209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/3ae4f87341d02c8bd3795cbae3fb4ca2.avif?t=1772358209\" width=800 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/8ae1b9ea4dbe77707344b3a2e5ce3894.poster.avif?t=1772358209\" width=900 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/8ae1b9ea4dbe77707344b3a2e5ce3894.webm?t=1772358209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥄 70+ 顾客特性，每位食客都有自己的口味</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥓 140+ 美味（有时也很离谱）的食材</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥗 90+ 遗物小帮手，解锁更多疯狂组合</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧀 商店系统，扩充你的厨艺军火库</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌶️ ️ 5种不同难度与13种初始套装</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/8ac7b4f2db4107cd1b71b29b0fa7bf92.poster.avif?t=1772358209\" width=900 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/8ac7b4f2db4107cd1b71b29b0fa7bf92.webm?t=1772358209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205380/extras/8ac7b4f2db4107cd1b71b29b0fa7bf92.mp4?t=1772358209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
